    <h1>Field validation and accessibility</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Bare minimum to meet accessibility re=
quirements</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Preferred from accessibility perspect=
ive, but not critical</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td rowspan=3D"4" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Numeric fields (eg Amou=
nt, BSB)</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Add an</strong> <strong>ARIA tag</str=
ong> for the screen readers to say <strong>only digits allowed</strong> and=
 the <strong>maximum number</strong> of digits allowed.</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Show a</strong> <strong>help text</st=
rong> telling the user only digits are allowed and the maximum number of di=
gits allowed.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Stop</strong> the user from entering =
any non-digit characters. Any non-digit characters will be ignored.</p></td=
>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Stop</strong> the user from entering =
any non-digit characters. Any non-digit characters will be ignored.</p>
<ul>
<li>Show an error message when user attempts to enter any non-digit charact=
ers will be ignored.</li>
</ul><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>'Maxlength' </strong>can be applied. =
When the user has reached the number of character limit, any input will be =
ignored.</p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>'Maxlength' </strong>can be applied. =
When the user has reached the number of character limit, any input will be =
ignored.</p>
<ul>
<li>Show an error message telling the user they have reached the number of =
character limit.</li>
</ul><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Copy/Paste:</strong> When copying/pas=
ting:</p>
<ul>
<li>any non-digit characters will be automatically <strong>stripped out.</s=
trong></li>
<li>if the number of character limit is reached, automatically <strong>trun=
cate.</strong></li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Copy/Paste:</strong> When copying/pas=
ting:</p>
<ul>
<li>any non-digit characters will be automatically <strong>stripped out. </=
strong>Show a warning message telling the user characters that are not allo=
wed were stripped out.</li>
<li>if the number of character limit is reached, automatically <strong>trun=
cate. </strong>Show a warning message telling the user the text was truncat=
ed because they reached the limit.</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td rowspan=3D"4" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Text fields (eg Credit =
description, Account number):</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Add an</strong> <strong>ARIA tag</str=
ong> for the screen readers to say what characters are allowed/not allowed =
and the <strong>maximum number</strong> of characters allowed.</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Show a <strong>help text</strong> showing cha=
racters allowed/not allowed and the <strong>maximum number</strong> of char=
acters allowed.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Let</strong> the user enter <strong>a=
ny characters including those not allowed</strong>. When the user enters an=
y characters that are not allowed:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>on leaving the field</strong>, show an <strong>error message</s=
trong>.</li>
</ul><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Let</strong> the user enter <strong>a=
ny characters even those not allowed</strong>. When the user enters any cha=
racters that are not allowed:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>on leaving the field</strong>, show an <strong>error message</s=
trong>.</li>
</ul><p><br></p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>'Maxlength'</strong> can be applied. =
Show the =E2=80=98remaining characters=E2=80=99 on long text. When the user=
 has reached the number of character limit, any input will be ignored.</p><=
p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>'Maxlength'</strong> can be applied. =
Show the =E2=80=98remaining characters=E2=80=99 on the text. When the user =
has reached the number of character limit, any input will be ignored.</p>
<ul>
<li>Show an error message telling the user they have reached the number of =
character limit.</li>
</ul><p><br></p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Copy/Paste:</strong> When copying/pas=
ting:</p>
<ul>
<li>allow <strong>any characters including those not allowed</strong> to be=
 pasted.</li>
<li>if the number of character limit is reached, automatically <strong>trun=
cate.</strong></li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Copy/Paste:</strong> When copying/pas=
ting:</p>
<ul>
<li>allow <strong>any characters including those not allowed</strong> to be=
 pasted.<strong> </strong>Show an error message telling the user they enter=
ed characters that are not allowed.</li>
<li>if the number of character limit is reached, automatically <strong>trun=
cate.</strong> Show a warning message telling the user the text was truncat=
ed because they reached the limit.</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
